# IconContainer

Welcome to my `Icon` component.

## Installation & Import

```bash
yarn add @ids-ts/icon-container
```

```tsx
import { IconContainer } from '@ids-ts/icon-container';
```

## Props

| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| `children` | `ReactNode` | Yes | Icon component to wrap. |
| `size` | `'small' \| 'medium' \| 'large'` | No | Container size. |
| `automationId` | `string` | No | Test automation identifier. |

## Token Usage

### Color

**icon** — Icon fill and stroke colors
- `--color-icon-accent`
- `--color-icon-complementary`
- `--color-icon-disabled`

### Size

**icon** — Standard icon dimensions

## Usage Patterns

### Explorer

```tsx
() => {
  return (
    <>
      <B1>
        The icon search tool is available at{' '}
        <Link
          href="https://icons.app.intuit.com/search"
          type="inline"
          target="_blank"
        >
          icons.app.intuit.com/search
        </Link>
      </B1>
      <iframe
        src="https://icons.app.intuit.com/search"
        title="Icon Explorer"
        style={{
          width: '100%',
          height: '100vh',
          border: 'none'
        }}
      />
    </>
  );
}
```

